metadata.name: TO THE MOON
metadata.description:
NFT & Web3 is the future. 
With Twitter being the home of crypto; Creators and Collectors alike, engage with each other without boundaries.

The Dead hidden tree  and the leaf represents life similar to web2 where Creators are shadow banned, despite having their artworks trending and under the limelight.

The Fog represents a future beyond belief, which awaits everyone trading in the blockchain. One NFT can literally change the course of a Creator or a Collectors life.
